      "page-details__main-about-jesse": {
        "type": "page-details__main-about-jesse",
        "blocks": {
          "73f6cc40-ebab-4526-aa71-7f68084bc68e": {
            "type": "image_with_text",
            "settings": {
              "image_position": "left",
              "image": "shopify://shop_images/AKCloset-Heritage_411502b3-51c2-442c-957b-b14e6cc77d01.jpg",
              "image_crop": "none",
              "title": "Anne Klein’s Granddaughter<br> Jesse Gre Rubinstein",
              "heading_size": "regular",
              "text": "<p>In 2018, Anne Klein’s Granddaughter, Jesse Gre Rubinstein, founded the Los Angeles/New York female-led Hello There agency which has launched innovative marketing campaigns and led digital strategy for numerous global brands.</p><p>In April 2020, we united with Jesse to deliver over 100,000 masks to essential workers during the height of the COVID-19 pandemic.</p><p></p><p>In May 2020, The Anne Klein Brand tapped Jesse to host the Women Who Do Series and this fall, Jesse will offer curated collections for the brand.</p>",
              "button_label": "",
              "button_style": "button--primary",
              "alignment": "left",
              "vertical_position": "center",
              "background": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
              "text_color": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
