      "page__loyalty-faq-accordion": {
        "type": "page__loyalty-faq-accordion",
        "blocks": {
          "fe3d7620-6ead-4f10-9613-72768fb40da6": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "How do I sign up for the AK Insider reward program?",
              "watches_header": "How do I sign up for the AK Insider reward program?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Signing up is easy! </p><p></p><p>Simply create an account <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/account/register\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/account/register</span></a> and enter your name, email, and password. It’s free to join and you will automatically be signed up to receive emails with insider access to sales, promotions, and all of our newest drops. If you currently have an account or email subscription with us - you’ve already been enrolled in our rewards program so you can kick back, sign in, and start earning Points!</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "dd4370a5-f5a1-43cb-9d05-499945d35d54": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "What are the advantages of becoming a rewards member?",
              "watches_header": "What are the advantages of becoming a rewards member?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Members receive rewards points for each purchase, that can then be redeemed towards the cost of merchandise.</p><p><br/>You also earn points for sharing <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/</span></a> with friends, following us on social media, leaving product reviews, and you are even gifted with bonus points just for having a birthday! You can view the full list of perks on our rewards page.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "46c3c864-2a8b-42d9-a8d8-89d0a1e56da3": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "How can I get a birthday reward?",
              "watches_header": "How can I get a birthday reward?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Add your birthday under ways to earn points on the <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards</span></a> . On your birthday we will send you a special discount code via email valid for 30 days from the date of your b-day!</p><p></p><p>*Your birthday code is non-transferable and may not be sold or assigned to anyone else. If we feel someone is trying to manipulate the program, we reserve the right to terminate your account at our discretion.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "d9aec8fd-f4ee-4cc1-bf03-b54980b1aaf9": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I signed up for the Birthday Bonus but I didn’t receive it?",
              "watches_header": "I signed up for the Birthday Bonus but I didn’t receive it?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Happy Birthday!  We’re so glad that you have chosen to celebrate with us through our rewards program.  In order for you to receive your birthday bonus on your birthday, you must register your birthday at least 30 days prior to your birthday.  <br/></p><p>All successive birthday bonuses will be emailed to you on your birthday.  If you register your birthday through your rewards account any time after it has passed in the current calendar year, rewards will not be added to your account until the day of your birthday in the following year.  </p><p><br/>Remember, the birthday reward is determined by the Rewards member tier that you are part of on the date of your birthday.  If it has been more than 30 days since you registered for your birthday reward and you still have not received the additional points in your account, please contact<span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span><a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/contact\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">customer service</span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span> and we will be happy to assist you.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "bc0377db-ce14-4973-9486-5566b17856ca": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I already have an account. Do I need to create a new one to earn rewards?",
              "watches_header": "I already have an account. Do I need to create a new one to earn rewards?",
              "paragraph": "<p>No, just login into your account.</p><p></p><p>All customers with an active account were automatically enrolled in our rewards program. If you have had more than one customer account with us, please note that only one rewards account was created per person.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "599ca837-5050-42cb-a45d-4e82f69b3af9": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Where can I find all of my rewards account info?",
              "watches_header": "Where can I find all of my rewards account info?",
              "paragraph": "<p>The rewards page is your roadmap to all your points and perks. You can access all your info by visiting our rewards page <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards</span></a> </p><p>And in your personal account.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "82262cbc-b0a1-4ebd-a3ff-222c04bf57c2": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Does it cost anything to begin earning points?",
              "watches_header": "Does it cost anything to begin earning points?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Absolutely not! Sign up is 100% free, and it will never cost you anything to earn points. Make sure to visit <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards</span></a>  to get started.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "9090ce0f-8271-427b-8df9-3ee1e8e55e87": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "How do I redeem my points?",
              "watches_header": "How do I redeem my points?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Exchanging your points for great rewards couldn't be easier! Simply visit <a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://anneklein.com/pages/loyalty-rewards</span></a> to view all of our great reward options and click the 'Redeem' to shop</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "ab2a0e02-80aa-45f3-af3a-46ab28f41fe4": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "How do points convert to dollars?",
              "watches_header": "How do points convert to dollars?",
              "paragraph": "<p>100 points = $10 dollars.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "26b1ed27-1eb4-40c5-90c6-22dd9a0727c8": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Will I be able to use my points/rewards in store?",
              "watches_header": "Will I be able to use my points/rewards in store?",
              "paragraph": "<p>No, Anne Klein does not own physical stores. Point rewards can only be redeemed on Anneklien.com</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "faq_U99Ueh": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "",
              "watches_header": "",
              "paragraph": "",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "6c7ec739-c547-4e28-b792-727243f84640": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Can I return my order if I redeemed rewards points for a discount?",
              "watches_header": "Can I return my order if I redeemed rewards points for a discount?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Yes. If you are returning the entire order, we will refund you the total dollar amount spent after the discount was applied. The points you used to redeem the discount will also be added back into your rewards account.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "4f8f9830-10d2-42bf-a985-c07dc556c162": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I've earned points with my last purchase, but now I want to return it. What will happen to my reward?",
              "watches_header": "I've earned points with my last purchase, but now I want to return it. What will happen to my reward?",
              "paragraph": "<p>If you use your rewards towards a purchase and later decide to return that item, your rewards will be credited back to your rewards account. For example, if you use a $10 coupon towards a $100 purchase that you decide to return, the $90 balance will be refunded on your credit card and the $10 reward credit will be deposited back into your rewards account.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "684fb339-5dae-40c8-af59-3ed02601bce1": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Do points ever expire?",
              "watches_header": "Do points ever expire?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Your points will expire one year after the date the points were earned</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "5b496246-be16-4a55-871e-98513871f10c": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "Why didn’t I earn points on my purchase?",
              "watches_header": "Why didn’t I earn points on my purchase?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Double-check you were signed into your rewards account and didn’t accidentally check out as a guest. You must be logged in when making purchases to earn points. If you have done this in error, contact us at <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span><a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/contact\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">customer service</span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span>to help apply your points to your account. You also won’t receive points if you return your purchase or your purchase is canceled for any reason. Please note that any points you earn on a purchase you later return will be deducted from your point balance.</p><p>Purchases made with gift cards will not be rewarded points. </p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "ecc44a95-2166-4131-9472-db29eacf2e6d": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I should have earned points for a purchase/incentive but I didn’t see my account balance change. Did I get credit?",
              "watches_header": "I should have earned points for a purchase/incentive but I didn’t see my account balance change. Did I get credit?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Yes! You work hard to earn points and we want you to feel confident that all of your points are right where they should be . . . in your account!  The first thing to note is that there may be a delay in our systems communicating and points could take anywhere from minutes to several hours to appear in your account.  However, if you feel like you have earned points but they are not showing up in your account you can also troubleshoot it with these tricks:</p><p>• Try to refresh your browser.</p><p>• Try to log out and then back into your account.</p><p>• Check your ‘Rewards history’ in your Rewards account to see if the points were added without you realizing it. Your ‘Rewards history’ will show you the number of points earned, how and when they were earned, as well as any redemptions of points made on your account.</p><p><br/>If you still feel like your points balance is not accurate you can contact our<em> </em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span><a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/contact\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">customer service</span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span> <em> </em>team and they will look into the issue for you.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "fc1d7009-ad7b-47d3-825f-4e7bdbc1bee3": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I received an error message when referring friends through the email referral box. What went wrong?",
              "watches_header": "I received an error message when referring friends through the email referral box. What went wrong?",
              "paragraph": "<p>We are sorry to hear that. Please check for email mistypes. There are a couple of scenarios that could have triggered the error message.  <br/></p><p>To eliminate confusion over what occurred, we recommend that you go back and enter each email address one at a time, clicking ‘send’ after each one rather than uploading them all at once.  </p><p><br/>If you are still having problems using the email referrals we recommend using your unique referral link or sharing the referral through Facebook, Twitter, or Messenger to receive credit. Please contact our <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span><a href=\"https://anneklein.com/pages/contact\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">customer service</span></a> if you need further assistance.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "5ddc5180-e0ae-45fb-8d80-e23e14c36001": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "I’ve referred several friends but haven’t received any points for it. Is there something else I need to do?",
              "watches_header": "I’ve referred several friends but haven’t received any points for it. Is there something else I need to do?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Thank you so much for sharing us with your friends!  We really appreciate it.  <br/></p><p>Points will be added to your account after your friend completes their first purchase on our website.  Please note it might take up to 24 hours for points to show in your account.</p><p></p><p>When this happens you will receive an email letting you know that one of your referrals made a purchase using your code and that a reward was added to your account.  You can also check your ‘Rewards History’ to see a list of any points that you have received for referrals.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "2b39743d-f236-49ac-8963-32f3622d8ca0": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_anchor": "How do I redeem my rewards at checkout?",
              "watches_header": "How do I redeem my rewards at checkout?",
              "paragraph": "<p>To redeem your points in checkout, use the drop down directly above your cart total to choose the amount you would like to apply, then click the \"APPLY\" button.<br/></p><p>You must have a minimum balance of at least 150 points each time you would like to make a redemption, and points must be redeemed in increments- first two 150 points to and following are 100 points.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          }
        },
