      "bcrf-text-top": {
        "type": "bcrf-text-top",
        "settings": {
          "title": "",
          "heading_font": "open_sans_n4",
          "heading_color": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
          "heading_alignment": "center",
          "heading_size": 20,
          "text": "<p>The month of October is Breast Cancer Awareness Month, and it’s a month that means a lot to the Anne Klein family. Our founder, Anne Klein herself, unfortunately passed away at the age of 50 due to breast cancer. As a brand Anne Klein is donating $10,000 to BCRF to help fund Breast Cancer research.</p><p>Make a donation while you shop to further the great work that BCRF does all year. Anne Klein is donating $10,000 to BCRF to help fund Breast Cancer research.</p>",
