      "page__faq-homegoods-accordion": {
        "type": "page__faq-homegoods-accordion",
        "blocks": {
          "4e6472dd-4c4d-4e98-a61b-24b6e3bef2bc": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Product Assembly",
              "watches_anchor": "Product Assembly"
            }
          },
          "41fa6811-02d3-4b6a-9231-7eb4c50382d3": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Do products come assembled?",
              "paragraph": "<p><strong>Products that require assembly</strong></p><p>Bed frame with drawers</p><p>Bookshelf on headboard</p><p>Dining set of a table and chairs</p><p><strong>Products that require minor/quick assembly</strong></p><p>Sofa/loveseat whose legs need to be attached</p><p>Nightstand/chest/dresser, whose drawer handles need to be attached</p><p><strong>Ready open-the-box-and-enjoy products</strong></p><p>Accent chairs</p><p>Set of dining chairs nested in a box reversely.</p><p><strong>Each unit will come with an instruction manual or a guide inside the product and tools needed.</strong></p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "13aa29db-4a35-4eda-bfda-7409b7cd70ab": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Where are the instructions to assemble?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Please find the assembly instructions in the product boxes.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "2b52b8ea-d5a4-4407-895f-092af4a3c0dc": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Are the tools included to assemble?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Yes, tools are included with all furniture pieces that require assembly.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "d5b6ee45-33a9-4a56-99ce-cba07f95faeb": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Returns",
              "watches_anchor": "Returns"
            }
          },
          "9fb62f9e-c325-4be1-850f-b711c4c16a4d": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Are home goods products orders eligible for a return?",
              "paragraph": "<p><strong>All furniture, towels and sheets are final sale</strong></p><p>All rugs are eligible for return within 30 days of delivery. To process a return please click on this link <a href=\"https://www.inreturns.com/anneklein#/\">https://www.inreturns.com/anneklein#/</a>  or reach out to customer service <a href=\"mailto:furniture@anneklein.com\">furniture@anneklein.com</a></p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "588832ca-00e0-4da9-99fc-aed9805c8567": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "What if I received damaged merchandise?",
              "paragraph": "<p>We take every possible measure before shipment to get the item delivered safely. If damage happens beyond control but is repairable we have a team of repair professionals across the country that will come to your home to repair. If the item is not fixable we will ship a new unit to you. No matter what furniture orders must be accepted upon delivery. If an order is returned to us because of refused delivery we will charge the appropriate return cost and deduct from refund.</p><p>Step 1: Document any concealed damages with photos and note the damage on the POD before signing, ie, box has been tampered with.</p><p>Step 2: Document any unconcealed damages with photos, i.e., chipped, dented or scratched items.</p><p>Step 3: Please contact <a href=\"mailto:furniture@anneklein.com\">furniture@anneklein.com</a> within 48 house of delivery of any order issues.</p><p>Step 4: Expect a response from customer service within 24-48 hours for next steps to see if you are eligible for a replacement or if your item is repairable.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "9ce98432-dcec-427e-8fa7-5ea1077141ec": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Warranty & Replacement Pieces",
              "watches_anchor": "Warranty & Replacement Pieces"
            }
          },
          "6348a132-967e-4ea3-b5b9-1857c19e21a9": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Can I add a warranty plan to my furniture order?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Yes, you can add a 2 or 3 year Mulberry Protection Plan to any furniture order.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "b5e1246e-eaaf-4b4a-be9f-bd135cfdf069": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Can I get a replacement piece if there are any product defects?",
              "paragraph": "<p>If your order comes with a damaged piece, please reach out to <a href=\"mailto:furniture@anneklein.com\">furniture@anneklein.com</a> with photos to determine if a repair or replacement is needed.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "aad40d44-25f4-487b-817f-36647b48b925": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "What if my order is missing pieces?",
              "paragraph": "<p>If there are missing parts/components, we will send what is missing as soon as possible. Please reach out to <a href=\"mailto:furniture@anneklein.com\">furniture@anneklein.com</a> for assistance.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "e8ff74b8-4aa9-4a14-a9f6-be84c2f77258": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Product Care",
              "watches_anchor": "Product Care"
            }
          },
          "20af8ac7-afa4-411e-bc4a-877d585170da": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "How to do I care for my product?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Please go to the product page under “How to care for product” to find care instructions. </p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "7e5fec56-e389-4b52-bfe3-4179879ddb58": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Shipping Options and Rates",
              "watches_anchor": "Shipping Options and Rates"
            }
          },
          "cd84591a-636e-4440-a784-c6b4a1371003": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Are furniture and rugs eligible for free shipping?",
              "paragraph": "<p>No, furniture and rugs do not qualify for free shipping.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "a4f5b35a-316e-4d6e-bd7e-cff1d3275dff": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "What locations do you ship to?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Anneklien.com ships to all 50 states including U.S. Territories provided that it is a physical address. We do not ship to PO Box, or APO/FPO or Internationally currently. (APO military address + FPO Fleet Post Off which is also associated with military.)</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "eac21632-15d9-4528-add2-0405ffb9dfa5": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "What are furniture shipping options and rates?",
              "paragraph": "<p>You can expect your furniture to be delivered in 7-10 business days after you receive an order confirmation. We currently only ship furniture with standard shipping.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "0b27224d-e1b2-41df-9c8a-d98f1a0aa87b": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "Is a signature required at delivery? Is delivery required to be scheduled?",
              "paragraph": "<p>Yes, a signature is required at the time of delivery. Once the order arrives at the last terminal, the shipping company will contact you and arrange an appointment date.</p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          },
          "9cc60094-2c37-4c67-9f22-c035aea99c54": {
            "type": "header",
            "settings": {
              "header": "Order Status",
              "watches_anchor": "Order Status"
            }
          },
          "855530d2-12ad-4557-8958-3a4ef37c1a18": {
            "type": "faq",
            "settings": {
              "watches_header": "How do I check the status of my order?",
              "paragraph": "<p>At the time you place your order on AnneKlein.com, we will send you an Order Confirmation email.</p><p>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a shipment notification which will include your tracking number. </p><p>If you have an account on AnneKlein.com you may also sign in to your account and view Order Status and History.</p><p><strong>Ownership of packages turned over to USPS/UPS/Fedex transfers to the buyer. AnneKlein.com is not responsible for lost, held, or damaged packages if a claim is denied by courier service.  We are not responsible for mis-delivery errors via carrier, or incorrect shipping info.</strong></p>",
              "margin": 0
            }
          }
        },
